---
import { Button } from "@/components/starwind/button";
import { Card, CardContent } from "@/components/starwind/card";
---

<Card size="sm" class="border-blue-200 bg-blue-50/30">
  <CardContent class="grid gap-3 md:grid-cols-[1fr_auto] md:items-center">
    <div>
      <div class="text-sm font-semibold text-neutral-950">AIBOUXシリーズ連携</div>
      <p class="mt-1 text-sm leading-6 text-neutral-600">
        Coreの帳票、Mailの添付、Shopの商品画像を、FILEの共有・変換履歴とつなげていく構成です。
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
      <Button href="https://mail.aiboux.com" variant="outline" size="sm">Mail</Button>
      <Button href="https://shop.aiboux.com" variant="outline" size="sm">Shop</Button>
      <Button href="/core" variant="outline" size="sm">Core</Button>
    </div>
  </CardContent>
</Card>
